{"tid":1152564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國人優先就診 中國民眾怒批共產黨「犯賤」","createTime":"2019-05-13T05:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T06:47:11.000Z","uid":28765,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8ba2be98f09d594bb2f1ac3cca1a708328f8ffa0","tid":1152564,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T05:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phplFMTj2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phplFMTj2.jpg&h=91af8157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國網友批評，共產黨就是犯賤，才會讓外國人優先就診。（圖擷取自微博）<br />\n<br />\n2019-05-13 00:07<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國江蘇省無錫市、南京醫科大學附屬無錫人民醫院近期內引發中國網友不滿，在該院就診櫃台寫著「台灣同胞，優先就診」，中國民眾對此批評共產黨「犯賤」，且此情況據悉從去年至今都沒改變。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php08Q8wU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php08Q8wU.jpg&h=2772e341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國江蘇無錫人民醫院讓外國民眾優先看診，引發該國本國人士不滿。（圖擷取自微博）<br />\n<br />\n中國網友自2018年12月30日起，陸續在微博貼出中國江蘇省無錫人民醫院櫃台照片，當中能見2張告示牌，分別寫著：「友善提醒，請攜帶身分證，實名制就診」、「離休幹部、台灣同胞，優先就診」，此事今（12）日被轉貼至中國臉書社團「帝吧中央集團軍」引發議論。<br />\n<br />\n中國網友們痛批共產黨不公，紛紛留言指出「共產黨犯賤你們是第一天才知道嗎」、「制定這個規定的醫院領導全家死光」、「這尼瑪啥幾把（78）醫院」、「一群畜生，把自己人不當人看，別人會把你當人看」、「一定是跪台辦的政策」、「什麼狗屎醫院」、「我去你的傻逼醫院」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2788156\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2788156&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=aa120ba4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2788156&h=a4210e9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2788156</a>"},{"pid":"b413c2be2dc45d4438dafa8288cda176e9d75905","tid":1152564,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T05:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f20ed3c60905b5dd39c7b973af0001250d89058","tid":1152564,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T06:43:36.000Z","msg":"係咪因為中國人成日走數？"},{"pid":"4c63d3864bf93e77d65ba9edeb444e36d9a0932a","tid":1152564,"uid":48458,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T06:46:05.000Z","msg":"乜又唔當台灣人係中國人咩<br />\n中國人畀中國人睇先天公地道<br />\n大家包容下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d6d5c56f923a625590b7c60095ddcec0cc049a","tid":1152564,"uid":60635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T06:47:11.000Z","msg":"香港人係中國都算外國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}